The events will feature WWE Superstars Braun Strowman, Seth Rollins, Dean Ambrose, intercontinental champion Roman Reigns, RAW women’s champion Alexa Bliss, Sasha Banks, Asuka, as well as RAW tag team champions Cesaro and Sheamus. <img src="http://c.biz-file.com/c/1712/422196.jpg" alt="WWE Superstars to tour SA in 2018" width="564" height="342"> “Following the overwhelming demand from our fans in South Africa, we are excited to return to Cape Town and Johannesburg, and bring WWE Live to Pretoria for the first time,” said Stefan Kastenmüller, senior VP and GM of WWE Africa, Europe and emerging markets. “WWE fans in South Africa can look forward to spectacular, non-stop, family-friendly entertainment featuring their favourite WWE Superstars.” Tickets for WWE Live South Africa will be available for purchase from 9am on 13 December 2017 on bigconcerts.co.za and computicket.com.